&lt;!-- ---

And the [eLife press release](https://elifesciences.org/for-the-press/3726fdd0/computer-model-can-process-disparate-sources-of-clinical-data-to-predict-brain-age ) by Emily Packer.
 --&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To get an overview on the paper, consider this Twitter thread:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote class=&#34;twitter-tweet&#34;&gt;&lt;p lang=&#34;en&#34; dir=&#34;ltr&#34;&gt;I am very excited to share our latest work published in &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/eLife?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;@eLife&lt;/a&gt;! We combined &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/hashtag/MEG?src=hash&amp;amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;#MEG&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/hashtag/fMRI?src=hash&amp;amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;#fMRI&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/hashtag/MRI?src=hash&amp;amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;#MRI&lt;/a&gt; for &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/hashtag/BrainAge?src=hash&amp;amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;#BrainAge&lt;/a&gt; prediction &amp;amp; &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/hashtag/biomarker?src=hash&amp;amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;#biomarker&lt;/a&gt; development. Each modality added unique information &amp;amp; enhanced brain-behavior mapping! &lt;a href=&#34;https://t.co/iCLYKsuUWY&#34;&gt;https://t.co/iCLYKsuUWY&lt;/a&gt; Thread👇 &lt;a href=&#34;https://t.co/dNEMlGnqXe&#34;&gt;pic.twitter.com/dNEMlGnqXe&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;mdash; Denis A. Engemann (@dngman) &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/dngman/status/1262676819775557633?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;May 19, 2020&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
